column5: Oldies but goodies. Still good laughs.

Man, I feel better now, I pulled one like that, shin kissed the trailer tongue, although it didn't feel bad at the time I ended up going t the hospital a couple hours later. It looked like I had a grapefruit growing out the side of my leg.  Doc said yep, it's a bruise, a good one.  give it time the blood will drain into your foot, he's right, it's purple.  And it still hurts like ..well can't use any of them words here.  I'd have to use a camera with panavision to get that lump all in one photo.
The very reason I removed mine Erich.Heck,what use do I have for it anyways?
Bill Dance with the shin guard hitting the receiver?  I thought it was funny when I was 10, lol.
